edu.harvard.integer.service.persistance

Interface PersistenceServiceInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseServiceInterface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PersistenceService

    public interface PersistenceServiceInterface
extends BaseServiceInterface
    The persistence service is started when the server starts. This will load any data that needs to be loaded. The data loaded is listed in the DataPreloadData table.
